query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('algebraic-number-theory',
'analytic-number-theory',
'cv.complex-variables',
'differential-topology',
'ds.dynamical-systems',
'finite-groups',
'homotopy-theory',
'inequalities',
'lie-groups',
'measure-theory',
'mp.mathematical-physics',
'oa.operator-algebras',
'probability-distributions',
'st.statistics',
'stochastic-processes');
